# Phase 28 (v0.9.99 SURF-04/D-16) -- build-time generated catalog snapshot.
# scripts/package-extension.mjs regenerates extension/catalog/recipe-index.generated.js
# from catalog/ before zipping; it is a deterministic build artifact (like the
# vendored .min libs are sourced, but this one is emitted) and would go stale if
# committed. background.js tolerates its absence in a dev tree. Never enters git.
extension/catalog/
